there are 3 types of traversing the trees 

- inOrder 
	1 / traverse the left subtree
	2 / visit the root
	3 / traverse the right subtree

- preOrder
	1 / Visit the root
	2 / Traverse the left subtree
	3 / Traverse the right subtree

- postOrder 
	1 / traverse left
	2 / traverse right
	3 / visit root

		2
	4		1
7		    8	    3

inOrder  ( from the left subtree -> root -> rightSubTree ): 7 4 2 8 1 3
preOrder ( from the root -> left subTree -> rightSubTree ) : 2 4 7 1 8 3	
postOrder : 7 4 8 3 1 2		


